The invention discloses digital television channel switching method and system, belonging to the technical field of digital television set-top boxes and solving the problems of channel switching blindness and lower efficiency of a traditional channel switching mode. The method comprises the following steps of: firstly, initiating a channel switching request, overlaying a channel switching interface home page on a current playing program picture, dividing the home page into a plurality of display areas, and displaying the program video preview of latest viewed channels in each display area; then, selecting and confirming a channel to be switched on the channel switching interface and finishing channel switching; and finally, storing a channel switching operation record. In a mode of displaying the program video preview of the latest viewed channels on the channel switching interface home page, the invention overcomes the channel switching blindness and improves the efficiency without influencing the normal playing of the current program.
